companyName: Invesco DWA Emerging Markets Momentum ETF
description:
The investment seeks to track the investment results (before fees and expenses) of the Dorsey Wright® Emerging Markets Technical Leaders Index (the "underlying index").
 The fund will invest at least 90% of its total assets in the equity securities that comprise the underlying index. The underlying index is comprised of equity securities of large capitalization companies based in emerging market countries.
